title: Super Mario Bros.
description: An NES classic that has stood the test of time! Everybody knows Mario.

title: The Legend of Zelda
description: Start it all with the original Zelda game! Control Link as he saves Hyrule from the clutches of the evil Ganon.

title: The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past
description: A legendary SNES entry into the storied Zelda franchise. Take Link through time to save princesses and slay Ganon (again)!

title: Fire Emblem: Geneology of the Holy War
description: Never released in English, this modified cartrige lets you explore and fight for Jugdral for the first time!

title: Final Fantasy VI
description: The last Final Fantasy game released on the SNES, Final Fantasy VI takes you on an adventure with Terra, Locke, Edgar, and many more!
